[background arg="#000000ff" fade="0.8"]
join Red? center
join Main center
if {StarlightRake} == "false":
	Red?: Oh you're a new face? Who are you wondering these woods?
	- I'm {MC}
		Red?: {MC}? That's a name I suppose...
		set {RED_Name} = true
		Red: Pleasure to have met. I'm Red. Is there something you needed?
		- I was trying to get out of the woods...
			Red: Ah and the gate is locked?
			Red: Yes I am sorry about that. Unfortantly the gate is to remained locked until further notice.
			Red: You see a...."Friend" of mine has stolen some property of mine, and I know she will try to escape if I unlock the gate.
			Red: So until that moon headed bastard gives me back my damn rake that gate will remained locked.
			Red: Ah so you know her than? Figures she seems to know damn near everyone here....
			- Starlight?
				Red: Oh you know her? Figures she can worm her way into everyone's life.
				Red: What did she tell you? That she bought the rake off me? That she's borrowing it? That she bought it herself?
				Red: What lie did she tell you?
				- She didn't mention a rake...
					Red: She...didn't even mention the rake...
					Red: my FAMILY HEIRLOOM RAKE!
					Red: that moon headed BASTARD!
					Red: ...
					jump rake help
			- A rake?
				Red: Yes a rake.
				Red: I know from your face that you are judging me. Its a family heirloom I'll have you know!
				Red: That theif Starlight must have taken it from me I just know it....
				jump rake help
	label rake help
	Red: .......
	Red: ...hey I think I know how we can help eachother here.
	Red: If I talk to Starlight than one of us is going to murder the other, and I do not want to deal with the fallout of murdering that bastard.
	Red: So how about you go and get my rake back?
	Red: What do you say
	- sure.
		Red: Perfect!
		Red: Come back when you have my rake and I'll open the gate for you.
		set {getRake} = "true"